\f1\b energy
\f0\b0  sectors on a diet while providing a glut of funding for fossil fuel development. \
The President's proposed budget calls for $19 billion in 2002 -- $700 million, or 3 percent below the 2001 budget -- for the Department of 
\f1\b Energy
